snippet: A vacationing employee of the United States Department of State, Victoria Tcaciuc, 38, was found strangled in a Rio de Janeiro hotel, the police said Thursday.
lead_paragraph: A vacationing employee of the United States Department of State, Victoria Tcaciuc, 38, was found strangled in a Rio de Janeiro hotel, the police said Thursday.

headline.main: Brazil: U.S. State Department Employee Strangled at Hotel
